{"id": 1279, "genre": 1001, "title": "你整理照片有什么习惯？", "description": "我，一个有20G杂乱照片的girl。（题图来自：Peter Oumanski）", "record_count": 2175, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161017175923FdhelIwfsixupVn2.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-24T03:00:59Z", "options": [{"id": 126976, "content": "每一年 每一次旅行 都要分类整理出来放在一个U盘里", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807572}, {"id": 127232, "content": "手机没内存，不存照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733028}, {"id": 128000, "content": "照照然后删删…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806723}, {"id": 126977, "content": "按时间，来源分类", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806099}, {"id": 127233, "content": "没有意义的就删  拍得丑也删  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777373}, {"id": 126978, "content": "我初中毕业后就开始了连上WIFI，打开微云然后什么都不管的愉快生活～", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191455}, {"id": 127234, "content": "常常删除。不删除照片的都不是非洲没存机\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 126979, "content": "为什么要整理?", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794759}, {"id": 126980, "content": "定期备份，而且要多备几份", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 655266}, {"id": 127236, "content": "之前没有整理一词，后来发现想找照片找不到，现在开始整理了，每次活动的会整理到一个相册上传原图到云盘里，把差不多的删掉！！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740031}, {"id": 159749, "content": "删删删删?????", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919339}, {"id": 126981, "content": "地点，时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740782}, {"id": 130821, "content": "以前有网盘所有照片一股脑上传，现在就只保存好看的发社交网络或者留一些纪念价值高的照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 822513}, {"id": 126982, "content": "没怎么整理", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792876}, {"id": 127240, "content": "整理是什么？干嘛的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652314}, {"id": 126986, "content": "手机显示内存不足的时候才会想着去整理照片", "image": "img/option/option/20161024141146hbu81Cw9ED6L0JfM.gif", "praise_count": 212, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799527}, {"id": 126987, "content": "只有我一个人不习惯iphone的相册风格吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 801185}, {"id": 126988, "content": "懒得整理，而且各种移动硬盘都放。有一次尴尬的是帮老婆找照片，一起的文件夹里还有各种小片子……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197409}, {"id": 126989, "content": "以前有，现在没了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807625}, {"id": 127245, "content": "按颜值", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759535}, {"id": 128013, "content": "直接传到网盘清手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809289}, {"id": 134414, "content": "上传到爱相机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414491}, {"id": 127246, "content": "建文件夹，建文件夹", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760287}, {"id": 126991, "content": "把不要的删掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807557}, {"id": 127247, "content": "手机自己“整理”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3365}, {"id": 126992, "content": "懒癌患者里面塞满了各种垃圾照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807298}, {"id": 127248, "content": "没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685181}, {"id": 131089, "content": "上传网盘然后删", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 822787}, {"id": 126993, "content": "用google photo 语意搜索。比如搜：去年在黄山的照片，和老婆在海边的合影等，搜完了找到文件名在硬盘里可以找到源文件", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805340}, {"id": 127249, "content": "内存满啦。就随便删一删\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128725}, {"id": 143122, "content": "一定会归类放照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863792}, {"id": 126994, "content": "很有必要！\n当然某些照片可以删除，一般每张照片背后都有故事．\n只是想说说看：有没有帮助整理分类的软件？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607337}, {"id": 127250, "content": "不怎么拍人，只爱拍风景食物什么的！比较好整理", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788799}, {"id": 127506, "content": "全部上传百度云", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797801}, {"id": 126995, "content": "自己一个文件夹，其他都按照时间和关系程度划分", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601736}, {"id": 127251, "content": "手机内存不足，全部打包扔进电脑，就是这么简单粗暴", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805174}, {"id": 129299, "content": "照片有大概30张后全部存入空间，然后删删删！空空的相册觉得很棒呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817314}, {"id": 126996, "content": "按时间比如2014 2015 2016，再加地点。时间线及地方来整理。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 801007}, {"id": 127252, "content": "相机里的照片都是按yyyymm＋地点来分类的，手机的照片却只有一个文件夹，以文件夹都是以导入时间建的，全放在一起，完全不想打理", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708922}, {"id": 126997, "content": "按个体来分类 自己的 合照的 集体的 风景的-…… 等等……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726413}, {"id": 127253, "content": "批量删除", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632917}, {"id": 126998, "content": "生活类事件线索\n人像时间加姓名\n观念类系列或项目为线索", "image": "img/option/option/20161024144937yL9zpPHFU2eZwcoY.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759294}, {"id": 127254, "content": "全选，delete", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594373}, {"id": 126999, "content": "看着好看的都存着，过一段时间全删了。就酱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803052}, {"id": 127255, "content": "换了新手机就喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799662}, {"id": 127511, "content": "定期整理 和备份保存\n毕竟有些人有些事回不去了 但是它还在 可以证明", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810303}, {"id": 128279, "content": "随时照随时删", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 813991}, {"id": 136984, "content": "把它们按不同类型存到空间云盘邮箱等等各种备份相册，然后就再也没翻过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846770}, {"id": 127000, "content": "以前仗着存储大从不整理，后来存储不够用了，就删掉拍坏的和无聊不够精彩的，现在换新手机了还是没改掉删照片的习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 208999}, {"id": 127256, "content": "没用就删", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808200}]}